## Server ##
0. Go to `server` directory.
$ cd server

1. Compile
$ make

2. Run server
$ ./server

## Client ##

0. Go to `client` directory.
$ cd client

1. Compile
$ make

2. Connect to server
2.1 Open a new terminal.
2.2 Connect to server with port number 1500.
$ ./client [IP] 1500
ex) ./client 127.0.0.1 1500

3. Input message and press `enter`. Then the other clients can get that message.
